description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20 Min Fat Burning HIIT Workout - All Standing, No Jumping, No Equipment' from the channel Oliver Sjostrom.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: 20 minute fat burning HIIT workout! All standing, no jumping, and no equipment. Perfect for a low-impact, full-body session to burn calories at home.
